    "We adopt the method of fused score and softmax calculations [39].",
    "The softmax values are computed row-wise and appropriately scaled to get the actual softmax for the attention head.",
    "This ensures that the attention values are computed without the need to write intermediate matrices back to DRAM, preventing frequent DRAM data access.",
    "The finetuning computations (LoRA) are also performed on the systolic array.",
    "Following MHA, the activations are transferred to the ReRAM for FF network processing."
